{"tid":1378944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［極重要］綜合多個關於撤定唔撤嘅Post，得出咗呢個結論","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T15:22:43.000Z","uid":53803,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6663700eb13e1ddb77dc1b63f1ebce5e35642e62","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"首先，要感謝各位前線嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於撤定唔撤嘅問題，其實呢兩日都好多討論<br />\n尤其係呢兩日落單嘅手足特別多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少一個就少一個<br />\n連登出現咗少少分化：<br />\n一邊覺得<span style=\"color: orange;\">交俾前線決定</span><br />\n一邊覺得<span style=\"color: green;\">冇勝算走先，下次再戰</span><br />\n其實兩邊都係同路人，我唔想見到義士係前線辛苦一大輪，翻到屋企仲要係連登罵戰<br />\n但叫撤嘅人亦不無道理，因為冇人想義士落單<br />\n<br />\n我綜合咗各個post嘅言論，得出咗以下結論：<br />\n<br />\n點解咁多巴絲想前線走先？唔計三毛搞分化，其實大部分都係唔想有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n所以：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有目標想衝嘅話，請唔好叫人走，真係交俾前線決定，因應當時環境決定撤唔撤</span><br />\n<br />\n但係，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果冇目標嘅話，就唔好死守打陣地戰，不妨交個場俾和理非，或者轉打遊擊，放大翻敵人嘅錯打文宣，亦可以減少被捕機會</span><br />\n<br />\n其實好多例子佐證：<br />\n612 有目標 就係衝立會，所以唔應該叫人撤，應該留到達成目的為止，達成目的後再因應現場環境撤<br />\n<br />\n621 圍警總，其實冇目標，因為我地係唔會衝警總，目的只係做下雞蛋撞石牆嘅抗議，記者影曬相，就可以撤<br />\n<br />\n71 有目標 要入立會，所以唔應該叫人撤，要留到達成目的為止，當然入左去走定留就交俾前線決定，目標係佔領，就留，目標係入去抗議，就適當時候撤<br />\n<br />\n光復屯門上水，有目標，要趕走大媽水貨佬，做完野基本上就可以俾前線決定幾時撤（或者轉打遊擊）<br />\n<br />\n沙田旺角夜，冇目標，純粹守，所以應該快撤，唔好落單<br />\n<br />\n上一次上環，有目標，圍中聯辦，所以應該留，支援勇武，交俾前線決定幾時走<br />\n<br />\n今日上環，冇目標，所以應該撤<br />\n<br />\n我明有義士覺得唔可以俾狗咁快清到場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我想俾到前線一個信息：<br />\n如果你地做緊嘅野係冇乜目標，純粹想消耗警力，或者消耗警力就係根本目標<br />\n心態不妨轉為遊擊/撤退<br />\n<br />\n不好同警犬硬碰，其實今日兩次速龍衝擊後，<br />\n係打得幾好，不斷係小巷走來走去，啲防暴就係好多耗損，睇到最後班狗係攤曬係路旁休息<br />\n你估咁熱著咁厚衫加重gear唔辛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一要諗就係點打速龍，不過我地優勢係人多，<br />\n佢衝過黎咪同佢死過，後排防暴一定唔會開槍，<br />\n唔係就會TK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住，做所有野都要有目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撤同唔撤係自古以黎兵法嘅要點<br />\n但冇目的下守陣地只會益左對家<br />\n所以大家一家要智取！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"22a8e7ed3633a17a02dbdf183f9016311e0f707d","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:10:10.000Z","msg":"希望有更多巴絲豐富呢個理論<br />\n唔洗再為呢個話題爭執"},{"pid":"a7a9154d883142e9bf034d431c7c2801666ac5e5","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a81ffc9b925ecbb289e2c6ec989c7a9efdc22690","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:17:45.000Z","msg":"推下啦"},{"pid":"b93ace0ea22680b99301a9f3499a1c8a23eb93f3","tid":1378944,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:22:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7557661dbd0080c0884a5e4eb884da1b8a79a787","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:22:57.000Z","msg":"有目標，不撤不散<br />\n冇目標，遊擊消耗警力"},{"pid":"80815f2b33585bd10b8f49619357c8f7899e6297","tid":1378944,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"新增<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必要裝備</span></span></strong><br />\n和理非: 一人一支強光or激光電筒 (對付速龍, 速度冇反光可阻視線)<br />\n前線: 波子/油 , 防速龍快速推進"},{"pid":"08798efbc05f44ccfe35fd2a9542613ce37693ef","tid":1378944,"uid":85857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:24.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8e9a3c757cbc9f20f1138d34b2ccd5280a0ee983","tid":1378944,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新增<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必要裝備</span></span></strong><br />\n和理非: 一人一支強光or激光電筒 (對付速龍, 速龍冇反光可阻視線)<br />\n前線: 波子/油 , 防速龍快速推進</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c50c3915e585f049bbd8529d959fa225d9225b6","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80815f2b33585bd10b8f49619357c8f7899e6297","tid":1378944,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"新增<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必要裝備</span></span></strong><br />\n和理非: 一人一支強光or激光電筒 (對付速龍, 速度冇反光可阻視線)<br />\n前線: 波子/油 , 防速龍快速推進"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"希望波子真係得<br />\n而家要解決嘅就係跑狗同橡膠子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0938b6fc10e69e2a6a89f442e3637d71bba2085","tid":1378944,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:25:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ad12067e35375a997e61d543375333d95b5f001","tid":1378944,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c50c3915e585f049bbd8529d959fa225d9225b6","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80815f2b33585bd10b8f49619357c8f7899e6297","tid":1378944,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"新增<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必要裝備</span></span></strong><br />\n和理非: 一人一支強光or激光電筒 (對付速龍, 速度冇反光可阻視線)<br />\n前線: 波子/油 , 防速龍快速推進"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"希望波子真係得<br />\n而家要解決嘅就係跑狗同橡膠子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"有電筒同波子, 已經牽制到跑狗最主要作用.<br />\nANTI- RUBBER BULLET有待研究"},{"pid":"57e4ed737d02e3af7cb0233734f1f185813e0c03","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:27:02.000Z","msg":"屌 又諗起張超雄騎劫be water<br />\n叫人走先 下次再黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b77929126978cfa5dc4da310d2ecf7f8e46a58","tid":1378944,"uid":260814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"分析得好好"},{"pid":"7c9470c4f5bd1766d6e5df59e006ed0904eeafbb","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db3c1b16e0a28ef8c5253d7cee15fc2179bb306","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:30:44.000Z","msg":"有目標，不撤不散<br />\n冇目標，遊擊消耗警力"},{"pid":"2b5d79896fa3419d42a1a2dd59a924befb1afbf9","tid":1378944,"uid":201656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:33:12.000Z","msg":"屌 搵人屌下呢個前警司得唔得？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08a19ea24e7c0a5e47accdd76af61f80bbf71212","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:33:44.000Z","msg":"有目標，不撤不散<br />\n冇目標，遊擊消耗警力"},{"pid":"564b5f7aacbe560201d7a04787fa2312684d31c9","tid":1378944,"uid":31542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:31.000Z","msg":"推 同意 今日有啲位想叫前線人退一退<br />\n但唔夠膽開聲 驚比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf35e1e1ad8adf9f3977c845e53c5c2cb17f458","tid":1378944,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:26.000Z","msg":"幫推左先 大致認同<br />\n但實際上點樣打游擊要再有經驗累積<br />\n又或者唔太容易再有D有目標既示威<br />\n所以可能游擊將會成為我地既主要戰線？"},{"pid":"3d879a285b72fab9167629543995851da160b4ce","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cf35e1e1ad8adf9f3977c845e53c5c2cb17f458","tid":1378944,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:26.000Z","msg":"幫推左先 大致認同<br />\n但實際上點樣打游擊要再有經驗累積<br />\n又或者唔太容易再有D有目標既示威<br />\n所以可能游擊將會成為我地既主要戰線？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:40:29.000Z","msg":"其實今晚真係打得唔錯<br />\n（除左大量手足因速龍落單之外）<br />\n要有巷戰 加少許路障<br />\n<br />\n目標嘅話 中聯辦/今日有人提過icac<br />\n其實都ok"},{"pid":"54c1657b73c3e6bfd2d31eebbb2a58d225d318b5","tid":1378944,"uid":269963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:43:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd03c1ae33a9dcd7cc6fd4f262d7aa21ba90a112","tid":1378944,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:50:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"32b82300a93bc031fa1332ef09b9e0e89b013aa5","tid":1378944,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:59:10.000Z","msg":"有目標，不撤不散<br />\n冇目標，遊擊消耗警力"},{"pid":"97a6934b3324a1ba9b9035a1f5495b98566f2de5","tid":1378944,"uid":248225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:59:32.000Z","msg":"如果聽日佢哋開會話出咩解放軍，停水停電，停工，大家唔洗理，當佢鳩UP。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我最怕聽日係政府放軟小小態度，例如話林鄭辭職，又撤回法例甚至話畀普選等等。 <br />\n<br />\n我預計會有以下情況出現：<br />\n1. 有一班打手上水話要接受政府退步，運動要停止啦。 <br />\n<br />\n2.或者飯民又接受政府開出既條件。<br />\n<br />\n3.又或者社會媒體又吹和談風。<br />\n<br />\n由此至終，五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n最重要既係第五點，我地唔要中共開出既普選，要有美國監督下既普選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以今晚同聽日下午三點，文宣宣傳重申五大訴求，缺一不可。同時煲大今晚黑警罪行。<br />\n<br />\n咁辛苦走到呢步，唔可以因為政府小小甜頭而散。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特此預告！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378852/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378852/page/1</a>"}]}